===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally {{zh-l|*叜}}. {{Han compound|宀|火|又|t1=roof; house|t2=fire|t3=hand|ls=ic}} – hand holding a torch in the house – original form of {{zh-l|*搜|to search}}.

Since the clerical script, the top components {{zh-l|*宀}} and {{zh-l|*火}} have merged into the unrelated {{zh-l|*𦥔}}.

